    "body": "Can you be a bit more specific about what you mean by it doesn't work? What behavior do you observe?\n\nDo you want something more like:\n\n``` py\ndef excepthook(type, value, traceback):\n    ipshell.showtraceback((type, value, traceback), tb_offset=0)\n    tb = traceback\n    while tb.tb_next is not None and tb.tb_next is not tb:\n        tb = tb.tb_next\n    frame = tb.tb_frame\n    ipshell(msg, local_ns=frame.f_locals, global_ns=frame.f_globals)\n```\n"
  },
